Name: maptiler
Version: 1.0.3
Summary: Allows custom geohash bucket sizes and finding buckets in vicinity of given location
Home-page: https://github.com/nziehn/maptiler
Author: Nils Ziehn
Author-email: nziehn@gmail.com
